                  <p><button class="w3-button w3-padding-large w3-white w3-border" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=3&timestamp=1495979765&ver=1&signature=3Cc6w46cc5qXVaM01hNcB7LbP*9c143no5ny83FTH4i6Vpp9mIjlID*OSmr*hKKitZTMumqzrs8Vqcc6igy99Rm0QRA3dZEsyeP0GNRhAjkFZPz9RWfUhYrrgwnDqRPtBdmzDu0NuN95Hud8bBKi5gr*dkmsF6czxkDveaJzsYg="><b>认识教练 »</b></button></p>
                </div>
              </div><hr>
            </section>

            <!-- 我是 BosGal -->
            <section class="bos-girl-box">
              <div class="w3-card-2 w3-margin">
                <div class="w3-container w3-padding">
                  <h4># 我是BosGal</h4>
                </div>
                <ul class="w3-ul w3-hoverable w3-white">
                  <li class="w3-padding-16" href="http://bit.ly/2rd1iNB">
                    <img src="http://bit.ly/2rd4CIt" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
                    <span class="w3-large">这个姑娘拉了一票波士顿的运动女神，到底想干嘛？</span><br>
                    <p style="color:grey"><span>波士顿爱运动的妹子都在这！</span></p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="w3-padding-16">
                    <img src="http://bit.ly/2r27xD6" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
                    <span class="w3-large">元气少女的早餐长什么样？</span><br>
                    <p style="color:grey"><span>波士顿爱运动的妹子都在这！</span></p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="w3-padding-16">
                    <img src="http://bit.ly/2raT0DO" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
                    <span class="w3-large">波士顿慢跑+早午餐指南</span><br>
                    <p style="color:grey"><span>波士顿爱运动的妹子都在这！</span></p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <hr>
            </section>

            <!-- 活動回顧 -->
            <section class="event-box">
              <div class="w3-card-2 w3-margin">
                <div class="w3-container w3-padding">
                  <h4>活动回顾</h4>
                </div>
                <script src="//lightwidget.com/widgets/lightwidget.js">
                </script><iframe src="//lightwidget.com/widgets/e8e6da2cfd455108835373104697f446.html" scrolling="no" allowtransparency="true" class="lightwidget-widget" style="width: 100%; border: 0; overflow: hidden;"></iframe>
              </div>
            </section>
           </section>
         </div>
       </div>
     </body>
